      "description": "This car is in poor condition. It runs but has noticeable mechanical issues that will require attention \u2014 expect rough idling, hesitation, or other drivability concerns. The exterior shows significant wear including multiple dents, scratches, and faded or peeling paint. The interior is worn with damaged upholstery and signs of heavy use throughout. Best suited for a buyer comfortable with a project vehicle or willing to invest in repairs.",
